Dialogue: 8,0:01:51.23,0:01:52.86,Text - CN,,0,0,30,,蛋糕♥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:11.63,Text - CN,,0,80,670,,{\fs60\bord1.8}福福商店街圣诞节抽奖券
